verbose_text: XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR In this study, we reported elevation in PCDH17 expression results in the loss of dendritic spines, which might be able to explain the observed association of PCDH17 with multiple brain functions and to implicate a potential molecular and neuronal mechanism of PCDH17 involvement in the risk for mood disorders.
